  {
   "id": 15,
   "name": "SystemHub",
   "x": 28,
   "y": 28,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Crystal",
    "file": "rtp/Crystal.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 64,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "A System Hub crystal hangs in the air, humming.\nInterface with the System?"
    },
    {
     "type": "system"
    },
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "stage",
      "stage": 1
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "conditional",
       "cond": {
        "kind": "quest",
        "id": "awakening",
        "check": "stage",
        "stage": 2
       },
       "then": [],
       "else": [
        {
         "type": "quest",
         "op": "advance",
         "id": "awakening"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "SYSTEM: Catalogued. A nearby anomaly has been flagged for you, [designation]. Clear it \u2014 and be rewarded."
        }
       ]
      }
     ],
     "else": []
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 16,
   "name": "Mira",
   "x": 12,
   "y": 18,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "People1",
    "file": "rtp/People1.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "done"
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "You're finding your feet. Stay sharp out there \u2014 the System always is.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 0
       }
      }
     ],
     "else": [
      {
       "type": "conditional",
       "cond": {
        "kind": "quest",
        "id": "awakening",
        "check": "stage",
        "stage": 3
       },
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "You did it. The System already logged the kill, of course. It logs everything.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "Here \u2014 a little field medicine. Out there, you patch yourself or you don't get up.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        },
        {
         "type": "quest",
         "op": "complete",
         "id": "awakening"
        },
        {
         "type": "grantskill",
         "skill": "first_aid"
        },
        {
         "type": "heal",
         "what": "all"
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "Welcome to Dawnhearth, Awakened. Try to stay yourself.",
         "face": {
          "sheet": "People1",
          "index": 0
         }
        }
       ],
       "else": [
        {
         "type": "conditional",
         "cond": {
          "kind": "quest",
          "id": "awakening",
          "check": "stage",
          "stage": 2
         },
         "then": [
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "That thing's still prowling the east field. Put it down, then come back.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          }
         ],
         "else": [
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Easy, now. You just Awakened \u2014 the System pulled you up out of the dark, same as everyone in Dawnhearth.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "You'll feel it humming at the edge of your thoughts. It names you, ranks you, hands you power. That's [designation] to the System now \u2014 but I'll call you [name].",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Move with the arrows or the pad; press A to speak to folk and to examine things. Your menu holds your Status, Supplies, and the meters that keep you alive out there.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "The System will offer you the world. Take what you need\u2026 but every favor it does you, it watches a little closer. Keep an eye on your Surveillance.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "text",
           "text": "Go on \u2014 touch the crystal in the plaza and let it 'welcome' you properly. Then come back and we'll talk.",
           "face": {
            "sheet": "People1",
            "index": 0
           }
          },
          {
           "type": "quest",
           "op": "stage",
           "id": "awakening",
           "stage": 1
          }
         ]
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 17,
   "name": "TutorialFiend",
   "x": 34,
   "y": 24,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Monster1",
    "file": "rtp/Monster1.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 12,
    "rows": 8,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "touch",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "done"
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "The field is quiet now."
      }
     ],
     "else": [
      {
       "type": "conditional",
       "cond": {
        "kind": "quest",
        "id": "awakening",
        "check": "stage",
        "stage": 2
       },
       "then": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "A System-twisted creature snarls and lunges!"
        },
        {
         "type": "battle",
         "enemies": [
          {
           "key": "emberling",
           "level": 1
          }
         ]
        },
        {
         "type": "quest",
         "op": "stage",
         "id": "awakening",
         "stage": 3
        },
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "The threat is down. Mira will want to know."
        },
        {
         "type": "despawn"
        }
       ],
       "else": [
        {
         "type": "text",
         "text": "Something rustles in the grass \u2014 but Mira said to meet her first."
        }
       ]
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 18,
   "name": "NoticeBoard",
   "x": 24,
   "y": 28,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "NoticeBoard",
    "file": "rtp/NoticeBoard.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 3,
    "rows": 4,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "NOTICE \u2014 By order of the Vanguard: any soul who abandons the System\u2019s protection forfeits its aid. The Untethered are not to be sheltered."
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Scratched underneath, in a shaking hand: \u201cThey took Joran for going off-grid. He only wanted to be left alone.\u201d"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 19,
   "name": "Tessa",
   "x": 20,
   "y": 26,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Tessa",
    "file": "rtp/Tessa.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 3,
    "rows": 4,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "You just Awakened, didn't you? I can always tell \u2014 you still trust it.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People3",
      "index": 0
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "The System will offer you everything. Healing, classes, safe passage. And every time you take a favor, the Surveillance gauge climbs.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People3",
      "index": 0
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Watch that meter in your menu, [name]. When the System knows you too well\u2026 it starts deciding things for you.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People3",
      "index": 0
     }
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 20,
   "name": "OldBram",
   "x": 32,
   "y": 30,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "OldBram",
    "file": "rtp/OldBram.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 3,
    "rows": 4,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Heh. Another one, pulled up bright and shining. The System does love a fresh Awakened.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People2",
      "index": 2
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "I've lived a long time, child. Long enough to feel like I've watched this all happen before. The crystals. The eager new Subjects.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People2",
      "index": 2
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Nobody else remembers. That's the part that keeps an old man up at night.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People2",
      "index": 2
     }
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 21,
   "name": "Lys",
   "x": 22,
   "y": 29,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Lys",
    "file": "rtp/Lys.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 3,
    "rows": 4,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "conditional",
     "cond": {
      "kind": "quest",
      "id": "awakening",
      "check": "stage",
      "stage": 1
     },
     "then": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "So the crystal 'welcomed' you too. It's kind, at first. It was kind to my brother Joran, before.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 1
       }
      },
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "He stopped taking its favors. Started living off-grid, untethered. The Vanguard came for him in the night.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 1
       }
      },
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "They say the Untethered forfeit the System's protection. They don't say where the taken ones go. Please \u2014 read the board by the plaza.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 1
       }
      }
     ],
     "else": [
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "You're new. Be careful who you trust here \u2014 and what you owe.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 1
       }
      },
      {
       "type": "text",
       "text": "My brother Joran trusted too little, in the end. Go on, talk to the crystal. Then we'll see what kind of Awakened you are.",
       "face": {
        "sheet": "People1",
        "index": 1
       }
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "id": 22,
   "name": "Corwin",
   "x": 30,
   "y": 27,
   "graphic": {
    "sprite": "Corwin",
    "file": "rtp/Corwin.png",
    "frame_w": 32,
    "frame_h": 32,
    "cols": 3,
    "rows": 4,
    "single": false
   },
   "dir": "down",
   "trigger": "action",
   "through": false,
   "commands": [
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Vanguard Sentry Corwin. Stay tethered, Subject, and we'll have no trouble.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People4",
      "index": 2
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "The System protects those who let it. The Untethered \u2014 those who refuse its aid \u2014 are a danger to Dawnhearth and to themselves.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People4",
      "index": 2
     }
    },
    {
     "type": "text",
     "text": "Report anyone living off-grid. It's for their own good. \u2026That's the line, anyway.",
     "face": {
      "sheet": "People4",
      "index": 2
     }
    }
   ]
  }
 ]
}